sql:
SELECT lecture_id, duration, topic 
FROM lectures 
WHERE topic = 'Machine Learning' AND duration > '2 hours';

SELECT DISTINCT faculty.faculty_name
FROM faculty
INNER JOIN lectures ON faculty.faculty_id = lectures.faculty_id;

SELECT *
FROM students s
WHERE s.gpa > (SELECT AVG(gpa) FROM students WHERE batch = 2021);

external_knowledge:
- "courses" refer to the subjects taught in the academic program;
- "average grade" represents the mean grade of all students who took each course;
- "student count" indicates the total number of students enrolled in each course.
